{
  "id": "RAW_7d0589bf",
  "title": "突发：昂贵的新证据表明「规模即一切」并非真理",
  "url": "https://garymarcus.substack.com/p/breaking-expensive-new-evidence-that",
  "date": "2026-03-14 18:23:18",
  "author": "Gary Marcus",
  "siteName": "Marcus on AI",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p>Remember the good old days a few years ago when almost everybody thought that the royal road to AGI ws just spending more money on compute and data?</p>\n  <p>That hypothesis continues to go badly, as expensive experiments from two of the world’s wealthiest men have just shown.</p>\n  <p>On the hand, it’s become clear that Mark Zuckerberg’s <a href=\"https://www.nytimes.com/2026/03/12/technology/meta-avocado-ai-model-delayed.html?smid=nytcore-ios-share\">latest model at Meta is good but not great, and not what he was hoping for</a>.</p>\n  <div class=\"captioned-image-container\">\n   <figure>\n    <a class=\"image-link image2 is-viewable-img\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/10de9392-ee8a-4746-66fb-30cd8a796e00/public\" data-component-name=\"Image2ToDOM\"> \n     <div class=\"image2-inset\">\n      <picture><source type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://image.jido.dev/20260315002704_59f6c2af-f5de-411a-b679-58da4c4d99b3_1905x1382.png 424w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/00bbfa63-92ff-4385-b4c1-f04bc0751300/public 848w, https://image.jido.dev/20260315002704_59f6c2af-f5de-411a-b679-58da4c4d99b3_1905x1382.png 1272w, https://image.jido.dev/20260315002704_59f6c2af-f5de-411a-b679-58da4c4d99b3_1905x1382.png 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\"><img src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5839e016-3095-4b37-6c3c-b4fe7dc4ca00/public\" width=\"1456\" height=\"1056\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;src&quot;:&quot;https://substack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com/public/images/59f6c2af-f5de-411a-b679-58da4c4d99b3_1905x1382.png&quot;,&quot;srcNoWatermark&quot;:null,&quot;fullscreen&quot;:null,&quot;imageSize&quot;:null,&quot;height&quot;:1056,&quot;width&quot;:1456,&quot;resizeWidth&quot;:null,&quot;bytes&quot;:1977690,&quot;alt&quot;:null,&quot;title&quot;:null,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;image/png&quot;,&quot;href&quot;:null,&quot;belowTheFold&quot;:false,&quot;topImage&quot;:true,&quot;internalRedirect&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/i/190953692?img=https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f6c2af-f5de-411a-b679-58da4c4d99b3_1905x1382.png&quot;,&quot;isProcessing&quot;:false,&quot;align&quot;:null,&quot;offset&quot;:false}\" class=\"sizing-normal\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/278a594c-e7f1-4ea5-70d9-fa3ec9e8fa00/public 424w, https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!rw_t!,w_848,c_limit,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F59f6c2af-f5de-411a-b679-58da4c4d99b3_1905x1382.png 848w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/c24d0e1a-9d1a-4606-9bb6-7ba52614bb00/public 1272w, https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/5839e016-3095-4b37-6c3c-b4fe7dc4ca00/public 1456w\" sizes=\"100vw\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture>\n      <div class=\"image-link-expand\">\n       <div class=\"pencraft pc-display-flex pc-gap-8 pc-reset\">\n        <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container restack-image\">\n         <svg role=\"img\" style=\"height:20px;width:20px\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 20 20\" fill=\"none\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"var(--color-fg-primary)\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n          <g>\n           <title></title><path d=\"M2.53001 7.81595C3.49179 4.73911 6.43281 2.5 9.91173 2.5C13.1684 2.5 15.9537 4.46214 17.0852 7.23684L17.6179 8.67647M17.6179 8.67647L18.5002 4.26471M17.6179 8.67647L13.6473 6.91176M17.4995 12.1841C16.5378 15.2609 13.5967 17.5 10.1178 17.5C6.86118 17.5 4.07589 15.5379 2.94432 12.7632L2.41165 11.3235M2.41165 11.3235L1.5293 15.7353M2.41165 11.3235L6.38224 13.0882\"></path>\n          </g>\n         </svg>\n        </button>\n        <button tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\" class=\"pencraft pc-reset pencraft icon-container view-image\">\n         <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-maximize2 lucide-maximize-2\">\n          <polyline points=\"15 3 21 3 21 9\"></polyline><polyline points=\"9 21 3 21 3 15\"></polyline><line x1=\"21\" x2=\"14\" y1=\"3\" y2=\"10\"></line><line x1=\"3\" x2=\"10\" y1=\"21\" y2=\"14\"></line>\n         </svg>\n        </button>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div> \n    </a>\n   </figure>\n  </div>\n  <p>And in the very same week, Elon Musk has conceded that for all the gigantic models xAI has built, xAI was ”<a href=\"https://news.google.com/read/CBMinAFBVV95cUxPVEtuMXNXTXRHbmVmZWdmaU5DUlNhMUFpZWhHb1d4Y1prUDNRdjdTNjlCWXNvUmJ6SHl4T1BRdTR2RHdZMml4Q0pfZHJVOFNmUjkyWkFteUJsQUZnU2JNM2tRNnJObk1jVkRUMHo2Y056d0VYR1dnaXo4ZFFVcU43ZGFtNldFMDIxdlNhQ3B3Q1RLZnJEMlNaODZXLTQ?hl=en-CA&amp;gl=CA&amp;ceid=CA%3Aen\">not built right first time around</a>”. Instead most of the founders are gone, and Musk has said that the company “is being rebuilt from the foundations up”.<a class=\"footnote-anchor\" data-component-name=\"FootnoteAnchorToDOM\" id=\"footnote-anchor-1\" href=\"#footnote-1\" target=\"_self\">1</a></p>\n  <p>So much for pure scaling<a class=\"footnote-anchor\" data-component-name=\"FootnoteAnchorToDOM\" id=\"footnote-anchor-2\" href=\"#footnote-2\" target=\"_self\">2</a></p>\n  <p>Two of the most expensive scientific experiments in history. Sooo much money down the drain.</p>\n  <p>All based on <a href=\"https://open.substack.com/pub/garymarcus/p/the-new-science-of-alt-intelligence?utm_campaign=post-expanded-share&amp;utm_medium=web\">the strange and dubious-from-the-start religion of scaling-über-alles</a>.</p>\n  <p>In my 2020 article, <a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/2002.06177\">The Next Decade in AI</a>, I foresaw all this, and urged the field to start focusing on world (cognitive) models and neurosymbolic AI. Now, maybe, we can finally move on to those projects?</p>\n  <p>So much time, money, and energy was lost chasing hype.</p>\n  <p class=\"button-wrapper\" data-attrs=\"{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://garymarcus.substack.com/subscribe?&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:&quot;Subscribe now&quot;,&quot;action&quot;:null,&quot;class&quot;:null}\" data-component-name=\"ButtonCreateButton\"><a class=\"button primary\" href=\"https://garymarcus.substack.com/subscribe?\"><span>Subscribe now</span></a></p>\n  <div class=\"footnote\" data-component-name=\"FootnoteToDOM\">\n   <a id=\"footnote-1\" href=\"#footnote-anchor-1\" class=\"footnote-number\" contenteditable=\"false\" target=\"_self\">1</a>\n   <div class=\"footnote-content\">\n    <p>Elon’s concession also fits well with the theory offered here on Feb 3 that <a href=\"https://open.substack.com/pub/garymarcus/p/four-theories-about-the-spacex-xai?utm_campaign=post-expanded-share&amp;utm_medium=web\">SpaceX’s acquisition of xAI at $250 billion was a thinly disguised bailout</a>. You don’t pay $250 billion for a company that was built wrong from the foundations.</p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"footnote\" data-component-name=\"FootnoteToDOM\">\n   <a id=\"footnote-2\" href=\"#footnote-anchor-2\" class=\"footnote-number\" contenteditable=\"false\" target=\"_self\">2</a>\n   <div class=\"footnote-content\">\n    <p>Musk could —literally— have saved tens of billions of dollars, if he had asked me….</p>\n    <p></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "文章认为，Meta 和 xAI 最近的挫折削弱了纯粹的规模扩张叙事，并重新唤起了对世界模型和神经符号 AI 的关注。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "文章认为，Meta 和 xAI 最近的挫折削弱了纯粹的规模扩张叙事，并重新唤起了对世界模型和神经符号 AI 的关注。",
  "summary": "本文报道了 AI 领域的一个重要转折：Meta 和 xAI 在超大规模 AI 训练项目上的挫折为「规模即一切」的范式敲响了警钟。作者 Gary Marcus 指出，这些代价高昂的失败实验表明，单纯增加模型规模和计算量并不能保证智能的涌现。文章重新点燃了关于 AI 发展路径的讨论，认为世界模型（能够理解和模拟物理世界的模型）和神经符号 AI（结合神经网络和符号推理的方法）可能是突破当前瓶颈的关键方向。这对于 AGI 策略和投资方向都有深远影响。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Meta 和 xAI 的大规模实验遭遇挫折",
      "explanation": "两家公司在超大规模 AI 训练项目上的昂贵投资并未产生预期的突破，这表明单纯依靠规模扩张的策略可能存在根本性的局限。"
    },
    {
      "point": "「规模即一切」的叙事受到挑战",
      "explanation": "传统观点认为只要不断增加模型参数和训练数据，智能就会自然涌现，但最近的证据表明这种简单化的观点可能忽视了智能本质的复杂性。"
    },
    {
      "point": "世界模型成为新的研究方向",
      "explanation": "能够理解和模拟物理世界因果关系的「世界模型」被认为是突破当前 LLM 局限的潜在路径，这类模型可能具备更强的推理和规划能力。"
    },
    {
      "point": "神经符号 AI 重新获得关注",
      "explanation": "结合神经网络的感知能力和符号推理的逻辑严谨性的混合方法，可能是解决当前纯神经网络方法局限性的有效途径。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "规模扩张不是自然法则，而是一种工程假设。",
    "昂贵失败的实验比廉价的成功更能说明问题。",
    "我们可能正在接近纯规模扩张策略的收益递减点。",
    "世界模型和神经符号方法可能是通往更可靠 AI 的必经之路。"
  ],
